HEADWORD: corticosterone
<hw>corticosterone</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>any of several steroid
compounds secreted by the adrenal cortex; they are involved in
regulating water and electrolyte balance in the body.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

